# Root .gitignore. Each app (api/, apps/admin/) has its own .gitignore
# with tech-specific patterns (node_modules, __pycache__, .next, etc.).
# This file covers OS + editor + secrets that apply across the monorepo.

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Editors / IDEs ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Secrets: belt and suspenders ---
# Individual apps also gitignore their own .env variants, but a
# top-level pattern guards against a fresh secret dropped anywhere in
# the monorepo by mistake (e.g. during deploy tinkering). Match every
# .env* variant (including .env.production / .env.staging, which the
# old explicit list missed) while keeping tracked *.example templates.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
!*.env.example

# Private keys / certs anywhere in the tree.
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.p8
*.keystore

# --- Logs / tmp ---
*.log
tmp/

# generated during icon regeneration
brand-assets/__pycache__/
